{
  "stem": "27507.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I really don't remember going more north of there into this very crowded area in the-- no, I was [POLISH] and so on, but not further north.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, there was in-- in this place in [POLISH], it was relatively nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in-- all together, it was spring in '42, and things somehow seemed to be--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--a little bit better, not much better maybe, but a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were still surviving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, the population of the ghetto must have gone a little down because so many people died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So many people died of hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, of course, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- people, masses of people who died every day, particularly during the winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were-- as I said, there were those carts of the [POLISH], which were collecting masses of bodies everyday.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- so some of the-- the poorest and some of the beggars died, and natural deaths, if one can call it natural death, in those winters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was probably the conditions were a tiny bit-- for a while, they were a tiny bit better, better and more optimistic.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in spring '42, we really thought that things were slightly normalizing, if not better than normalizing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the other hand, the Germans started the war with the Russians-- with Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were very aware of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think most people were hoping that the Germans were== that Hitler was going to get eventually a bloody nose, that he was going to lose the war, but not everybody.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some people thought the Germans were going to win the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
